Overview:
BBC Consulting Planners is a Sydney-based specialist town planning consultancy committed to providing a wide range of quality managed urban and regional planning consultancy services.

We aim to:-

-  provide planning services to the highest professional standard;
- deliver services on time and at competitive rates;
- work proactively as a member of a project team with open and clear communication;
- consistently exceed clients'​ expectations;
- recognise and respect our staff; and
- adhere to principles of social and environmental sustainability.

Our services include a wide range of urban and regional planning and social planning services which are detailed under Company Specialties

We provide specialist planning input to development and project applications either as part of a large multi-disciplinary team where we are proactively involved as a key team player, or as the lead consultant co-ordinating and directing the input of a range of specialists and undertaking negotiations with consent or approval authorities.

